Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:09.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, he bets with other men's money!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:13.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに他人の金\N禁断の3000万に手を出した坂崎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:12.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki lays hands on the forbidden 30 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.16,0:00:18.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He dives back into a world of madness! Beyond all limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:18.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,極限を超えた狂気の勝負 再開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:21.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)\pos(640,505)}Heaven's Fall, Man's Fall
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:25.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けられない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.34,0:00:24.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.37,0:00:28.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃんの戦略は\Nもう風前の ともし火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:28.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pop's plans are at their very edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:30.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's like he's on a rope bridge about to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.87,0:00:34.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,崩れかけた つり橋だ\N見えている たどり着く前の崩落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:33.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He can see it! He can see himself fall before he makes it across!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:40.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも進むしかねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:40.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But still, he has no choice but to keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:43.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに橋 希望がある限り
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.17,0:00:41.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Following that bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:43.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,As long as he has hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:51.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:55.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめられねえよな\N失っちまったんだから 全財産を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:55.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's already lost all his money...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.83,0:01:00.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if he quits now! Even if that's the smart move!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:01:01.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たとえ今 やめたとしても\Nそれが賢明だとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:06.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その後 おっちゃんに\Nどんな人生が待ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.05,0:01:05.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What kind of life will he have after that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:13.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の仕事でもらった わずかな金で\Nあの暮らし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.47,0:01:11.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Living like that on the pittance he gets from his job?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:16.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つしかねえ　そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:14.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He has to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:15.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:18.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He has to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:19.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つしかねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:20.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝て おっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.07,0:01:20.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Win, pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:23.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,橋を渡って成し遂げてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:23.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Cross that bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:27.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちの悲願　リセット 再生を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.57,0:01:27.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,For our wishes! Our hopes! Our rebirth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:33.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki's begun to bet the extra money he scraped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:33.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,坂崎は急きょ用意したらしい\N追加金を使い始めました
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:36.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's about time for the block?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.81,0:01:36.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろブロックの頃合いかと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:40.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ まだ動いてなかったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:38.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:40.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You still haven't done anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:42.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい 申し訳ございません
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:42.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.78,0:01:46.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうせ追加の金は借金か\Nくすねてきた金
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.84,0:01:46.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He has to have either borrowed or just pocketed that extra money.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:51.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなのに手を出すってことは\Nもう戻る気はないのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:51.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If he's dipping into it, he has no intention of stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:52.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How shall I describe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:55.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うなら\N坂道を転がる暴走トラック
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.60,0:01:55.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's like a runaway truck, coming down the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:58.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The brakes have long since burnt away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:58.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ブレーキは とうの昔に\N焼き尽くしている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:02.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かっていても止まらない\N止めようがない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:02.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if he knows what's happening, he won't stop. He can't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.90,0:02:04.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大破するまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:04.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Until he wrecks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:11.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ブロックを躊躇する必要はない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:11.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no need to hold back with the block.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:13.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll set it up right away, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.01,0:02:13.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ では早速
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:24.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What a pitiful sight. He's not even interesting enough to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:24.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,醜い　どうでもいい こんな奴は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:27.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm more worried about who he dragged in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:27.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それよりも１匹\N紛れ込んでいるじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.59,0:02:29.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,名うてのギャンブラーが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That famous gambler...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:35.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵は まだ動いていない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:35.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They haven't made their move yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:38.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決めるなら 今しかねえ\Nおっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:38.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's now or never, pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:42.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The manager said...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長が あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:43.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:49.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ブロック発動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The block activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:54.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほれ\Nいけ 頑張れ　いけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:58.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっ？\N何か入らなくなったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's not getting any in anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:02.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クルーンに行ってねえ\N全部 あの役モノに弾かれてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:03:00.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Nothing's making it to the trays!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:02.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Everything's bouncing off the flippers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:10.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今まで３分の１は通していた\Nクルーンへの番人 急変
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:08.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The guardians of the trays had, until now, let one of three balls through!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:10.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But now, all that changes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:14.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弾く　閉ざす
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:13.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It shoots the balls back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:16.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The path to hope now closes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:16.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,希望の道を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:23.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit! They're up to something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:23.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ　何か やりやがった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:29.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:31.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:31.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:36.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これや　このランプが\Nセンサーになっとるんや
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:36.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This light... It's really a sensor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:45.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひでえ　こんなんありかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:44.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is terrible! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:48.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひどすぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:47.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:49.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:52.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん　もういい やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:52.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's enough! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:56.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クルーンに行かなきゃ\Nいくら打っても全部 死に玉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:56.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you can't even get to the trays, you're just wasting balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:05.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま… 待てよ　これ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:04.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait... This... This!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:07.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おー きた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:09.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？\N久々のクルーン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:10.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He finally got another one in the trays!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:12.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ\Nうおー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:13.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can do it, pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:15.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけるぞ おっさん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:17.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな　どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:17.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Impossible! How!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:27.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To the right! He's bouncing them off the right and getting them in that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:27.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右… 右打ち\Nおっちゃん 右に玉を流し込んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:33.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは…\Nきた！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:32.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:33.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:38.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また横道から！\N開かれた奇跡の道筋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:35.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He got it in from the side again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:38.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A path springs open, miraculously!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:40.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何てこった　ルートを外れた玉が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:44.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!? He's bouncing misses off the wheel and into the trays!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:45.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,車輪の回転で役モノの下を\Nくぐってクルーンに落ちている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:50.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの表情　奴らにとっても\Nこれは計算外なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:50.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If they're making that face... That means they never expected this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:51.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:53.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ってことは ひょっとしてあるかも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:54.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe he has a chance at the jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:57.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大当たり　大逆転勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:58.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He can turn it all around! A 600-million-yen miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:05:00.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,６億の奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ　いけ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:05.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,諦めるな　諦めちゃダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I won't give up! I can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:09.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吹いとるんだ 神風が
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The divine wind pushes me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:17.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That wind brings my dead balls back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:13.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その風が\N本来 落ちるしかない死に玉に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:19.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吹き込んでくれている 命を
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Another ten million!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:21.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう1000万だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:25.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに可能性はある
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:25.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He has a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:31.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが あのブロック前の好調さとは\N比べものにならない　おっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:29.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But the rate's still far lower than before the block.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:30.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:33.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神にも慈悲があるだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:33.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The gods must have some shred of mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:37.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これきり…\Nこれきりってことがあるか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:37.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is it! This is all I need!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:40.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと１回 あと１回はあるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:41.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One more ball! One more ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:46.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３段目のクルーンに行くことが\N行けば 行きさえすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:46.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I can just land one more ball in the third tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:51.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度こそ ねじ込む\Nこいつ 磁ビールで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:50.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This time I'll catch it with my magnetic beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:55.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし最初の数発こそ\N通ったものの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:55.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But even though his first few balls made it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:58.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その後は打てども打てども
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:06:01.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,after that, no matter how many he shot, the rest simply fell to the bottom of the machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:01.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,空しく回収穴に のみ込まれていく
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:05.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,希望　消える 消える
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:05.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His hopes fade! They fade!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:08.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,希望の玉 １玉4000円
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:09.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His balls of hope, at 4,000 yen each!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:15.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His nausea wells up, and!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:14.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こみ上げる吐き気
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:17.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして歪む 歪む
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It bends! It twists!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:20.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,溶ける 溶ける
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It warps, it melts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:23.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限りなく続く射精のような感覚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:23.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It feels like endless ejaculation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:27.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ぬ… 死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:29.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The balls, they fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:30.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛ぶ 飛ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:32.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,散る 散る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:32.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Only to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:36.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,光る 光る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:35.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It glows!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:42.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして最後の1000万
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:42.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And, he risks his last ten million!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:44.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:44.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:50.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,発射 発射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:52.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He fires again and again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:52.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,発射！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:58.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ある意味 桃源郷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:59.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In a way, this is his utopia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:04.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破天　破漢　破滅\Nそして至福へのカウントダウン
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:04.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The fall of heaven! The fall of a man! His ruin! A countdown to utter bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:08.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見るにたえない至福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A bliss he can't stand to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:10.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きたぞ おっさん\Nうん？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:09.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There you go, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:20.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった ２段目\Nいけいけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:19.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're at the second tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:31.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There it is! The third tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:32.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きた ３段目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:36.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに３段目　奇跡への入り口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:36.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He makes it to the third tray! Last stop before a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:41.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん　入れろ\N恐らく これが最後のチャンス
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:38.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Make it in, pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:41.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is probably your last chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:50.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む　入ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:49.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please! Go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:53.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,与えてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:53.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:58.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度 わしに\Nあの暮らし 日々を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:58.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll have my life back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:03.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神様　神様　神様
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:03.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,God... Oh God, oh God!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:06.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 緩くなってきたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:06.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's losing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:09.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この１周で決まる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:08.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:14.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:19.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I bend it here, I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:19.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで引き寄せれば勝てる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:21.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:21.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:30.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ　落ちろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go! Go in the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:44.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ\Nマジかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:44.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Seriously!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Aww man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:47.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなんありかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:47.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You were so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:50.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう少しだったのに\N惜しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:51.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:53.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's with that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:00.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:08:59.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:19.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん 大丈夫か\Nおっちゃん　おっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, pops!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:19.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops! Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:24.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ\Nおっちゃん… あ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:31.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご友人は大丈夫ですか？カイジ様
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:31.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Will your friend be all right, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:34.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつ どうして俺の名を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:34.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How does he know my name!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:38.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:42.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたは？\Nごあいさつが遅れました
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry I didn't introduce myself earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm Ichijou, the manager here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:47.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長の一条という者です\N以後 お見知りおきを
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm quite pleased to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:49.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:57.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ お諦めにならず\Nいま一度 勝負を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:57.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, now, you mustn't give up now. Take another try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:59.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？で… でも
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:09:59.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:05.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:05.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょ… ちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:07.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マズい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:06.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:10.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か？\Nあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:09.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:16.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最悪　最悪の展開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:16.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The worst! The worst possible thing which could happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:28.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:27.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:33.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ もう一勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:32.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:37.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな　どうして…\Nおっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:35.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Impossible! Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:39.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ この玉ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:39.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, these balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:42.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 今日はどっちだ？\Nはあ　真ちゅう製です
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Which ones are we using today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:43.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Brass balls, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:46.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ 真ちゅう？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:46.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Brass balls!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:50.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In order to avoid incidents with some of our more unsavory customers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:50.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当店では よからぬことを\Nたくらむ連中への防衛策として
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:52.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,磁石に反応する鋼鉄製と
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:56.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,along with normal steel balls we have brass balls which aren't affected by magnets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:56.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,反応しない真ちゅう製を\N使い分けています
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:02.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあさあ お客様　お気を確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:02.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:05.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだパッキーは残り600もある
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:05.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You still have six million packy left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:07.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大当たりの可能性は\N残されています
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:10.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can still hit the jackpot. Go on, chase your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:11.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,存分に夢を追いかけてください
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:15.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々は そのお姿を\N心から応援する者です
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:15.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We just love seeing players who aren't afraid to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:28.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,惨敗\Nこの日 坂崎の手元に残ったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:30.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,At the end of the day, Sakazaki is left with only 6.38 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わずか638万
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:34.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２時間あまりで4362万を失った
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:34.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In what seems like only a moment, he lost 43.62 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:39.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チクショー\N全部おとりだったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:39.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Goddammit! We get hoodwinked! Bamboozled!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:43.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The A-setting schedule... Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:42.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,釘設定の予定表も何もかも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:46.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悔しい… 悔しい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:47.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I hate it! I hate it!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:03.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:06.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほう そんなことがあったか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:06.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:11.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ　しかし坂崎も\Nあのカイジという男も しょせんは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:14.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, but Sakazaki and that... Kaiji, did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:14.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢事が自分の思いどおりに\N運ぶはずだ｣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:16.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,と思い込みたがる甘ったれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're both naive enough to still think they were in control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:18.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな輩に負けやしません
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:21.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course I won't lose to men like that. I was about to handle things quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:21.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何ら問題なく ねじ伏せました
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:28.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君はそういう言葉で\Nくくれるほど一筋縄じゃいかんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:28.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can't just write Kaiji off like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:31.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Really, Ichijou...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:33.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それどころか ある意味 一条 君を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:36.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In some ways, Kaiji is far superior to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:36.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君は はるかに凌駕する
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:43.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Be careful he doesn't trip you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:43.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ せいぜい足元を\Nすくわれぬよう気をつけることだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:49.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The ponies!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:51.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,競馬？\N４日後の競馬で
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:54.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we play the ponies in four days and work ourselves back up to 60 mil, we can try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:54.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残った金を6000万にすれば\Nやり直せる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:56.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本気で言ってんのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you serious!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:13:00.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ ここで一発 一発当てれば
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:13:00.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We just need to take one more shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:05.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと４日で残った金も\N消えちまうのか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:06.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Take those four days and just take the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:07.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… 何！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:07.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:10.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わりいこと言わねえから\N残った金持って
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:09.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:13.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Take the money you've got left and find somewhere in the third world to go live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:14.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,物価の安い外国へでも\N逃げたらどうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:16.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,縁起でもないこと言うな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:16.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:18.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい おっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:22.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,触るな　不吉 不吉　運が落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:19.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:22.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Your bad luck's gonna rub off on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着けって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:23.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:33.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日の玉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's a ball from yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:34.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:37.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待てよ　ひょっとすると
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:36.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That just might be—!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:40.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspiration flashes through Kaiji's brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:39.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脳裏を貫くひらめき　閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:43.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ？\Nこの玉 借りてくぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm borrowing this ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:47.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? Borrowing? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:47.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？借りてくって 一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:52.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to that casino. There's something I need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:49.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,例のカジノに行ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:52.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと確認したいことが\Nあるんでな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:59.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, entering the casino in the evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:14:00.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夕刻 カジノに入ったカイジは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:05.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,wanders around the Bog, as quiet as if yesterday had never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:05.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日の熱気がウソのように\N閑散とした沼の周りを漂い
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:07.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And he stares.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:10.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして眺め続けた 何時間も
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:10.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,For hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:20.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がつけば朝　午前８時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When he looks up, the sun has risen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's eight in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:26.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご友人が負けて\Nまだ一昼夜だというのに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:26.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's barely been a day since your friend lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:29.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And yet you seem like you'd like to give it another try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:29.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう やりたそうな風情ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:30.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:32.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に\Nちょっと失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:32.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then, if you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:43.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,朝の日課でね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I have my morning tasks to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:47.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私と主任が日替わりで\Nこいつの釘調整をするんです
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:47.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I alternate days with the maintenance man, adjusting the pins on this machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:51.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 何も\N毎日やらずともって話ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:51.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, they don't change every day so it's not every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:54.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But money is money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:56.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かかっている金額が\N金額ですからね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:15:00.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長である私が言うのは\Nはばかられるのですが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:15:00.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,As the manager, I hesitate to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:02.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,設定は当分Ｃです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:02.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,but of course it's usually set to C.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:03.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,C?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,Ｃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:09.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最もクルーンに到達しにくい設定\NそれがＣ設定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:09.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Setting C! The setting which makes it most difficult for balls to fall into the trays!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:11.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノーチャンスです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:11.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:19.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,At least for the two weeks you have left on the outside, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少なくとも
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:19.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたがシャバにいられる\Nここ２週間ほどはね カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:30.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Seems like you know a lot about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:32.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,随分と詳しそうだな 俺について
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:35.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No, nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:35.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいえ　知りませんよ 他には何も
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知る必要もないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:41.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,薄汚い野良犬の素性なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:42.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not about a filthy stray like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:52.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわー\Nそれホントの話か
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:52.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So you think he'll run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:54.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:55.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ホントですよ\Nそんなバカな客…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:03.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だお前 ここは立ち入り禁止だぞ\N用のない奴が勝手に…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:03.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you!? It says, "Do Not Enter"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:05.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you don't have any reason to be—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:05.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,—I have a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,用はあるさ\N何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:06.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:08.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体 何の用だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:26.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:27.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様…\N換金してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Cash me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:31.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１つ おっちゃんの服に\N紛れ込んでてね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:30.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I found this ball in the old man's clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:32.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:33.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな\Nよせ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:36.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は？\N換金してやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:36.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll cash him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.44,0:16:38.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は… はい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:37.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:55.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:53.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:59.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら これでいいだろ\Nさあ出ていけ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出ていけって言ってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:01.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I told you, get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうカリカリしなさんなって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:05.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeez, pull the stick out of your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:13.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Lemme have a smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:13.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一服くらいさせろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:16.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出てけ　今すぐとっとと出いてけ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:16.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Get out of here! Stand the fuck up and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:24.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君　そんなに珍しいですか\Nこの部屋が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:24.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Is this room really so intriguing, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:30.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をたくらんでるか知らないが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:32.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're planning, but let me give you this advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:32.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いことは言わない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:35.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの沼以外の\Nギャンブルにすることだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:35.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Try a game other than the Bog.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本来パチンコは\N台を支配している店側が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:41.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The house controls everything about pachinko machines. It's always a losing bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:41.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100％勝つギャンブル
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:45.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店が本気で出さないと\N決めた台では決して客は勝てない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:45.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we don't want it to pay out, the players aren't seeing a single yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:48.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かもしれねえな\Nかもじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:47.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No maybes about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:51.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,揺るぎない現実ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:51.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Nothing but stark reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:55.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうです　くだらぬ夢を見るより
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:52.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:58.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Forget those bullshit dreams and live for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:58.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたにとって貴重な今を\N楽しんでは？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:02.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の名刺を持って\Nこちらの店へ行けば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:02.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Take my card and go to this bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:04.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Drinks, food, everything will be on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:06.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,タダで飲み放題 食べ放題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:10.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're going to be spending a long time underground. May as well enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:11.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君がこれから送る\N長い地下暮らしの慰みにぜひ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:19.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What the fuck are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.14,0:18:20.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をする 貴様
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:24.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That feels even better than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:24.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初めてやったが\N思ったより気持ちがいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:29.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Especially if it's the card of a guy who just plain reeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:27.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが鼻持ちならねえ奴の\N名刺ってんなら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:31.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに格別　最高だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:32.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:35.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,野郎　貴様 ここから\N無事に出られると思うなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:35.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You think you're getting out of here with your kneecaps!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:38.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ\N店長 いいんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:36.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:38.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Really, boss!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:45.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I gave it to him. It's his to do with as he wishes, whether he should or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:42.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいも悪いも\N一度 渡した物をどうしようと
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:45.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もらった者の自由だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:48.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is his last chance to show a little spine, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:48.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たぶん これが\N最後の意地ってやつなんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:52.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Soon he'll be burrowing back down into the earth like a cicada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:54.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これからセミのように\N地の底へ戻る負け人間の
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:54.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:07.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バーカ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:06.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:13.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなチンケな名刺より\Nもっとデケえ土産を頂いたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:12.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I walked out of there with something a lot better than his lame business card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:33.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,位置的には一番奥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:33.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The furthest one in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:40.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ ６階 603号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:39.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The sixth floor. Room 603.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:42.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:43.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The power meter isn't moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,電気メーターも動いてない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:57.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし 空き部屋だ　やった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:54.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:56.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's an empty room!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:59.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけるかもしれねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:20:00.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know if this'll work, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:04.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少なくとも\Nあの釘の森 第１関門は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:04.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That forest of pins... That first barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:08.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突破できる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:08.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've got it beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:10.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji grasps it!
